parameters:
\nw[Mistress]You will earn 100G during the break. Will you take
a rest?

\nw[Taro]It's a mercenary group NTR. I received a job
request, but is the deal confirmed?

\nw[Mistress]Ah, are you from the mercenary group? I have heard
about the matter.

\nw[Mistress]Please wait at that seat. I will bring the client
with me.
\nw[Taro]Looks like I'll be kept waiting for a while.

\nw[Kuno]Nonna and I are also taking on another job from
Prae, so we need to discuss that too...
\nw[Taro]Another job? I haven't heard about that...

\nw[Kuno]I was told to talk about that after coming to this
city...

\nw[???]Thank you for coming. I appreciate that you
accepted the request.

\nw[???]Sorry, but I'll talk for a while without showing
my face. Let's do introductions when I reveal
myself.

\nw[???]This is part of the request. Please listen to what
I have to say for a while.
\nw[Taro]Is this part of the request...? Wait, as for me...
\nw[Taro]From the voice, it sounds like a woman, right?
\nw[Kuno]It sounds like a woman, doesn't it?

\nw[???]It's just idle chatter, so you can ignore it. It's
not important what the content is.

\nw[???]The problem is whether it's okay for you to listen
to my voice for a while. So please listen there.
\nw[Taro]Haa... What do you mean by listen to the voice?

\nw[???]I think I wrote the details when I made the
request, don't you know?

\nw[Taro]No, I was told that the details would be discussed
when we meet...

\nw[???]Tch... Did that guy do something? Well, if you
don't know, let's talk about that.

\nw[???]I am currently cursed. The effects of the curse
are manifesting in my voice.

\nw[???]That curse is said to make you horny when you hear
my voice. It seems that the effect becomes even
stronger when it's turned into a song.

\nw[???]The one who cursed me is a succubus. So I thought
that if it's a succubus or one of their minions,
they might not be affected by the curse of my
voice. That's why I sent a request to Prae, who is
a succubus.

\nw[???]So, what we're talking about now is a test to see
if you're affected by my curse. If it turns out
that just hearing my voice makes you horny, then
I'll pay you the cancellation fee and send you
home. How about it?
\nw[Taro]I see... For now, it seems like I'm fine, but...
\nw[Taro]Well, it seems like everyone is fine, huh?

\nw[???]Well, if you didn't have any resistance, you would
already be getting excited.

\nw[Shia]Nice to meet you, I'm Shia. I'm a woman who is
also known as the Songstress of Azure. Please take
care of me.

\nw[Taro]Ah, I'm Taro, the leader of the Mercenary NTR
Brigade. Nice to meet you too.

\nw[Shia]I'm sorry for doing something like testing you. I
should have already mentioned that when I sent the
request.

\nw[Taro]No, it's more like a communication error on our
end... or rather, I feel like Prae intentionally
didn't mention it, knowing that you would be
concerned.
\nw[Taro]So, is the request about lifting a curse?

\nw[Shia]Ah, that's right. One day, I was suddenly
enchanted by a succubus.

\nw[Shia]For a while, I didn't really understand... but
during one of my performances, everything got
messed up. And that's when I realized that it had
the effect of arousing people's voices.

\nw[Shia]So, I had it investigated and I also found out how
to solve it. But you have to go to a certain
place. I want to ask you all to be my escorts.

\nw[Taro]Escorting... Are we going to a strange place to
lift the curse?

\nw[Shia]I guess there's no other way since I don't know
much about magic. If you guys say there's an
easier way to lift the curse, then that would be
great.

\nw[Taro]No, that's impossible... We don't have any magic
researchers or anything like that.

\nw[Shia]The best magician in this country... I think
they're called a Witch. I heard that if I ask
them, I can pretty much solve everything, but I
can't meet them, and they ignore my letters. I
don't know what to do.

\nw[Shia]Since there was no other way, I asked for help and
investigated various things. And then, I found one
method that seems like it could solve it.

\nw[Shia]There is a small temple on the northern island
from Rimuru. It seems to be a temple with strong
water power, and it seems that special magical
water is accumulated there.

\nw[Shia]If we gather that magical power with a magic
sphere and put it into my body, the curse will be
lifted.

\nw[Shia]That's why I'm saying I'm not familiar with magic.
In the first place, you won't know how to solve it
unless you actually try to solve it. Just because
it's the same curse doesn't mean it can be lifted
in the same way.

\nw[Shia]I obtained the magic sphere on my own. So I'm
asking you guys to secure a means of
transportation to the island and provide
protection.

\nw[Shia]If the curse is lifted, then the request will be
finished. If it doesn't, I might ask for something
else as an additional request.

\nw[Taro]I understand the request. When you say securing a
means of transportation, does that mean we need a
boat?

\nw[Shia]Ah, that's right. Right now, just by speaking, I
can arouse the other person, so I can't even
negotiate with someone who can't read the words.

\nw[Shia]Besides, it seems that the sea monsters in these
waters have increased recently. Because of that,
there are talks about being afraid to set sail.

\nw[Shia]That's why I'm asking you guys to handle the
negotiations around there. Since you're a
mercenary group, you should be able to fight. And
if money is needed for the negotiations, I'll
cover it, but there is a limit.

\nw[Taro]I understand, we need to secure a boat and crew...
If we can secure them, we'll go to the temple on
the northern island with Shia-san.

\nw[Shia]It's Shia. Also, it seems that the temple on the
northern island is called the Water Temple.

\nw[Taro]I've been walking all day and just arrived in
town. Is it okay to start tomorrow?

\nw[Shia]If anything happens, let me know. I can't speak
even if I go out to town, so I'll mostly be at the
inn.
\nw[Mistress]Mistress, will you be taking a rest today?
\nw[Taro](Should I rest today and prepare for tomorrow...?)
\nw[Mistress]Please be careful as it gets cold at night.

\nw[Shia]Sorry, I'll leave the negotiations to you. If you
need any help, let me know.

\nw[Taro]Ah, actually, it seems that there is a large
outbreak of monsters in the sea. So, considering
the safety as well, I'm wondering whether we
should move right away or wait.

\nw[Taro]Can you give me your opinion on whether it's
better to move right away despite the danger, or
wait until the problem is resolved before heading
out?
\nw[Shia]We should go right away. Waiting is no good.

\nw[Taro]It might be dangerous, but is it okay? In terms of
safety, it would be better to wait, but...

\nw[Shia]You came to ask about my decision, right? I don't
care about safety, let's hurry and head to the
temple. That's my wish.
\nw[Taro]Ah, I understand. Let's proceed in that direction.

\nw[Taro](They seem to be in a hurry more than I thought...
But if that's the case, we'll have to find a way
to get the ship moving...)

\nw[Taro](Should I go outside the inn and consult with
Nonna and the others...)

\nw[Shia]I see. If you have any problems, let me know right
away.

\nw[Shia]The plan is to hurry as much as possible. I'm
counting on you.
\nw[Shia]Hmm, so it's the two of you. Alright, sit down.
マップ８８にあるイベント４のセルフスイッチAをオンにする

\nw[Taro]Ah, Shia, you can't speak in front of others,
right? You must be quite bored. That's why I
thought we could do something together for a
little while.

\nw[Shia]Are you planning to play together? I thought I
asked you to get a ship for me, did you forget?

\nw[Taro]No, I've left that to the other members for now. I
can't help you there until something happens. So I
have some free time.
\nw[Taro]I thought we could spend some time together.

\nw[Taro]Maybe if we spend time together, we might learn
something about the curse. So, until there's a
change in the negotiations for the ship, please
spend time with me.

\nw[Taro](Having a conversation might help relieve
stress...)
\nw[Shia]Ahh, yeah, that might be true. Alright, I got it.

\nw[Shia]Even if you say that, what do you plan on doing? I
can't speak outside, so basically I can't go out.

\nw[Taro]Ah, I've thought of something to do. That's why I
brought Uka with me.
マップ８８にあるイベント５のセルフスイッチAをオンにする

\nw[Shia]The thing we're going to do... is it teaching Uka,
right?

\nw[Taro]Surprisingly, you've adapted quite well. You can
read and do calculations to some extent.

\nw[Shia]In this country, education is compulsory, so I
went to school. I don't really want to remember it
though.

\nw[Shia]It's dangerous if you can't read and write,
especially when you're also involved in composing
music.

\nw[Shia]Why is Uka studying reading and writing now? She's
already an adult, right?

\nw[Taro]No, Uka doesn't know her age or anything. Even if
you ask her about the past, she's quite vague. It
seems she doesn't remember the exact passage of
time at all.

\nw[Taro]It's because appearances and age don't necessarily
match in magic and such, so it's hard to say. It
seems certain that she didn't receive an education
though...
\nw[Shia]Hmm, you're going through a lot of trouble.

\nw[Taro]I thought Shia would resist or dislike teaching so
easily.

\nw[Shia]Actually, I have a lot of free time. Now that
we've decided what to do, there's not much I can
do.

\nw[Shia]How about muscle training and building physical
strength... things like that? I can't be out of
breath outside, so let's do it indoors.
\nw[Taro]So, it's a cramped way of living, huh...

\nw[Shia]Hmm... food, huh. I haven't really thought about
it.

\nw[Shia]I'm sure there were things that I thought were
delicious... but I don't remember.

\nw[Shia]More than that, my head was filled with singing
and dancing.

\nw[Taro]Is it because of your profession...? Don't you
have any childhood memories? Surely you haven't
been writing lyrics since you were a child, right?
\nw[Shia]I don't remember things from such a long time ago.

\nw[Taro]I see. Well, if that's the case, there's nothing
we can do about it.
\nw[Taro](Do you dislike talking about your childhood?)

\nw[Taro]I thought about buying or making something if
there was something you liked.

\nw[Shia]The meals were always quick and easy to eat. As
long as it was easy to chew and filled my stomach,
it was good enough.

\nw[Taro]I see... How about we have hot pot? It might be
nice to try something we don't usually eat, right?
\nw[Shia]Hot pot... We don't usually eat that, do we?

\nw[Shia]Uka doesn't have much expression. Her voice is
also quiet... But she has good potential, so I
think she'll become even cuter if she's raised
well.

\nw[Shia]At first, a forced smile is fine, so something
like this.

\nw[Shia]Ah~ It's difficult to suddenly make expressions,
but if you train yourself to consciously move your
facial muscles, you'll be able to create
expressions.

\nw[Shia]If you do that, eventually you'll be able to
express your emotions through your facial
expressions.

\nw[Taro](Finally smiled... If things continue like this,
it seems like negotiations for getting the ship
will be fine even if they drag on...)

\nw[Taro](I wonder how Nonna's negotiations will proceed
from here...)
エロイベントでノンナが船長を堕とすことに成功し、
船を借りれるようになる。
船長の船を借りるために色仕掛けを仕掛ける

Nonna's Hospitality 2 is an event that you have
already seen once. Would you like to skip the
event?

Nonna is once again keeping the captain company
today. It's already been four consecutive days.

During that time, the captain was completely
captivated by Nonna, who listened to his
complaints and served him.

Nonna sat next to the captain and carefully
cleaned his penis. Then, she leaned against the
captain a little and peered into his face.
\nw[Nonna]...Captain, I have a favor to ask.

\nw[Captain]What is it? If it's a request from Nonna, I'll
listen to anything.

\nw[Nonna]Actually, I'm looking for someone who can take a
boat to the Water Temple located to the north of
here.

\nw[Nonna]So, I want you to let me ride on your ship,
Captain.

\nw[Captain]A boat, huh... But I'll need someone to deal with
the monsters...

As the captain seemed to be lost in thought, Nonna
brought her face close to his.

The influence of Nonna's scent and body
temperature can be seen as the captain's tongue
slightly extends from his nose.
\nw[Nonna]I want to see where the captain is working.

\nw[Nonna]Yes, I think it's wonderful to have a man who can
do his job well. Captain, you can do it too,
right?

\nw[Nonna]Leave the escort to me. The mercenary group I
belong to will be in charge of the escort.

\nw[Captain]If that's the case, I'll take care of it. Leave it
to me.

\nw[Nonna]Thank you, Captain. You're so kind, it's really
helpful.

As Nonna hugged the captain and said that, the
captain's breathing became rough. It seems like
he's extremely excited.

\nw[Captain]It doesn't matter how many monsters there are, as
long as it's my arm!

\nw[Shia]I'll get on the boat later, so please go ahead.

\nw[Shia]Thanks to the power of the succubus, I was saved,
but I'm still tired.
\nw[Shia]Please go to the harbor ahead of me.

\nw[Taro]Shia should be inside the inn, I need to meet her
and talk.

\nw[Fross]I heard from Nonna-san. You were about to depart
on a ship, right?

\nw[Taro](Come to think of it, I forgot to mention that I
would be coming later...)

\nw[Taro]Did you come alone? I thought it would be quite
dangerous on the way...

\nw[Fross]No, it's because Louis-san happened to come this
way, so we came together in a carriage. There was
also a woman who is an acquaintance of Louis-san
with us.

\nw[Fross]Louis-san wasn't fighting. In fact, there were no
monsters in sight.

\nw[Fross]Thanks to that, we arrived in one day. Well, it
became today because we adjusted the departure
time to match with Louis-san.

\nw[Taro]I see... Wait, if you came together, does that
mean Louis is also nearby?

\nw[Fross]No, he said he had some business to attend to and
went somewhere.

\nw[Taro](I wanted to talk, but... I guess it won't work
out conveniently)

\nw[Fross]You're going to the northern island, right? Please
call me when you go.

\nw[Nonna]I wonder what is needed for the ship's repair?

\nw[Captain]We have most of what we need, but we're missing a
special fruit that can be found in the western
Raulus Forest... We don't have enough Flaurus
Fruit.
\nw[Captain]If we have that, we should be able to repair it.
\nw[Nonna]I see... understood. We will go and gather it.

\nw[Captain]However, the crew members are also scared of this
incident. Even if the ship is repaired, whether we
can venture into the sea with monsters...

\nw[Captain]Even if it's for the sake of rescue, I can't just
send out the ship...

\nw[Nonna]I see... but is there anything I can do to help?
I'll do anything that I can.
\nw[Captain]...Oh, is there anything I can do?

\nw[Captain]Alright, let's have that conversation between the
two of us then. We also need to gather the Flaurus
Fruit.

\nw[Nonna]Yes, understood. Uka, can you gather everyone and
go pick it?

\nw[Fross]I tried examining Shia-san, but there doesn't seem
to be any health issues.

\nw[Shia]Did everyone come back? I want to talk about the
request, so please listen.

\nw[Shia]First of all, I want to express my gratitude for
rescuing me. Thank you.

\nw[Kuno]Well, I don't really deserve thanks... I did fail
at my job as a bodyguard from the start...

\nw[Shia]It's partly my fault for that matter, so it's
fine. Anyway, I want to talk about the original
request.

\nw[Shia]Regarding the request, it was originally supposed
to be an escort to the Water Temple, but since the
curse couldn't be lifted, it has turned into an
additional request. Is that okay?

\nw[Taro]Ah, for now, I'll listen to what you have to say.
Whether I'll accept it or not is a different
matter.

\nw[Shia]I failed to lift my curse, but it's good news that
I found a way to weaken its effects.

\nw[Shia]So, that woman in the maid outfit... was it Louis?
I wonder if she knows anything. Can we contact
her?

\nw[Taro]No, it seems even the owner Prae doesn't know her
contact information. She should be living outside
of Solte where we reside, but her personal
information is completely unknown.

\nw[Shia]So, if that's the case, there's no time for that
approach... In that case, there's another method.

\nw[Shia]Actually, my live performance is scheduled for one
week from now. Can you make sure that the curse
doesn't activate and that I can sing properly
during the live?

\nw[Taro]Speaking of ensuring that the curse doesn't
activate, you did say that you would be fine after
sexual activity, right?

\nw[Shia]Yeah, but it's only temporary. If the curse starts
to take effect while I'm singing during the live
performance, it would be unbearable, right?

\nw[Shia]We need to verify various things, such as how long
the curse can be suppressed after sexual activity,
whether any type of sexual activity is acceptable,
and how singing or performing affects the
duration.

\nw[Shia]I want you to verify that and ask for the
suppression of the curse so that it doesn't
activate during the live performance.
\nw[Shia]Is that the content? Is it okay?

\nw[Taro]A change in the request, huh... Well, since the
curse lifting has failed...

\nw[Taro]It seems like there is little danger and there is
no reason to refuse.

\nw[Kuno]So, does that mean you'll have a physical
relationship with Taro multiple times? Don't you
have any thoughts about that?

\nw[Shia]It's not like I have no reservations at all, but
if it's an effective means, then I won't worry
about it.

\nw[Shia]I want to have various experiences to broaden my
expression, and having sex with an incubus doesn't
come with the worry of sexually transmitted
diseases.

\nw[Shia]I want to try things I haven't experienced, not
just limited to sex. I honestly don't want to be
cursed anymore, though.
\nw[Kuno]Is that so? Yeah, I understand. Thank you.

\nw[Shia]Speaking of which, we should get back to the topic
of the request. We can't exactly do it in a place
where there are people, right? Since we'll be
singing and having sex.

\nw[Shia]So, I want you to prepare someone to verify the
curse in a place where there are no people. If
there's any other good method, that's fine too.

\nw[Taro]Verifying the curse... We can't do it right before
the live performance, can we? It needs to be
finished within at most 4 or 5 days...

\nw[Taro]I understand. I'll think about what to do. For
now, please take a rest today. You must be tired,
right?
\nw[Shia]Oh, sorry. Let me know if anything happens.

\nw[Taro]Let's go to the second floor and discuss what to
do...
\nw[Nonna]Oh my, going out at this late hour?

\nw[Taro]Oh, just a little bit. Is Nonna still getting
ready?

\nw[Nonna]Yes, I'm going to do the sales that Prae asked me
to. If the captain comes, I intend to get on their
good side so that I can negotiate well.

\nw[Taro]Ah, that's right. It feels strange for me to say
it, but I'm counting on you.

\nw[Nonna]Speaking of which, Taro was heading towards the
northwest. It's a place with only residential
houses, but I wonder if he knew someone there.

\nw[Taro]Is that so? Well, I don't know much about Thor's
social circle...
\nw[Taro]Is this the feeling of picking up customers here?

\nw[Kuno]That's right. Taro, if you're coming as a
customer, I'll welcome you, but...

\nw[Taro]Since we're lovers, there's no need for you to
pay.
